      "content": "ok that's helpful. i went down to the basement and i see a big post right under where that wall is. it looks like it's holding up the whole floor above. feels kinda scary to mess with something that crucial, like if i get it wrong the whole place could just collapse. what are the actual risks if i accidentally knock out a support?",
